  ### 🚀 How to Run Locally

        ```bash
        # 1. Clone the repo
        git clone https://github.com/your-username/crop-recommendation.git
        cd crop-recommendation

        # 2. Install dependencies
        pip install -r requirements.txt

        # 3. Generate dataset
        python data/generate_dataset.py

        # 4. Train models
        python src/train.py

        # 5. Launch app
        streamlit run app.py
        ```

